<div class="pageListContainer">


    <ul class="unstyled pageList">
        
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/2015-Kentucky-Winner%27s-Circle-schools-recognized.aspx'>2015 Kentucky Winner's Circle schools recognized</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl0_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">9/22/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            Today, ten Kentucky public schools are being recognized for outstanding teaching and learning conditions.&#160; See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R%2015-105%20TELL%20Winners%20Circle.pdf">news release</a> for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/Board-of-Education-to-hold-special-meeting.aspx'>Board of Education to hold special meeting</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl1_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">9/22/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            The Kentucky Board of Education has scheduled a special meeting for Wednesday, September 23 at 2&#58;30 p.m. ET in the state board room, 1st floor Capital Plaza Tower, 500 Mero Street in Frankfort. A live webcast of the meeting will be available <a href="/comm/Pages/Live-Streaming-Audio-and-Video.aspx">here</a>.&#160; See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R-104%20KBE%20to%20hold%20special%20meeting.pdf">news release</a> for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/Kentucky-awarded-grant-for-gifted-and-talented.aspx'>Kentucky awarded grant for gifted and talented</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl2_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">9/22/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            The Kentucky Department of Education has been selected to receive funding under the <a href="http&#58;//www2.ed.gov/programs/javits/index.html">Javits Gifted and Talented Students Education Act Program</a>.&#160; See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R%2015-106%20Javits%20Grant.pdf">news release</a> for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/Unbridled-Learning-Assessment-and-Accountability-briefing.aspx'>Unbridled Learning Assessment and Accountability briefing</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl3_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">9/22/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            In preparation for the 2015 release of data from Kentucky’s Unbridled Learning Assessment and Accountability System, the Kentucky Department of Education Division of Communications is holding a virtual briefing on Thursday, September 24 at 10 a.m. ET for media, school public relations staff and any other interested parties. See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R-107%20Unbridled%20Learning%20Briefing%202015.pdf">news release</a> for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/Students-encouraged-to-apply-for-Next-Generation-Council.aspx'>Students encouraged to apply for Next-Generation Council</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl4_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">9/10/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            Public school students in grades 10-12 are invited to apply for membership on the Next-Generation Student Council, an advisory group that provides input and feedback to the Kentucky education commissioner. See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R%2015-100%20Student%20council.pdf">news release</a> for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/State%27s-equitable-access-to-effective-educators-plan-approved.aspx'>State's equitable access to effective educators plan approved</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl5_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">9/10/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            The United States Department of Education (USED) has approved Kentucky’s plan to ensure equitable access to effective, engaging educators for all students.&#160; See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R%2015-101%20Equitable%20Access%20Plan%20Approved.pdf">news release </a>for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/24-Ashland-Inc.-Teacher-Achievement-Award-winners-named.aspx'>24 Ashland Inc. Teacher Achievement Award winners named</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl6_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">9/9/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            The Kentucky Department of Education and Ashland Inc. have selected 24 outstanding Kentucky educators as recipients of the 2016 Ashland Inc. Teacher Achievement Awards (TAA). See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R15-099%20Ashland%20teacher%20achievement%20awards.pdf">news release </a>for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/Number-of-students-taking-AP-tests-up-scores-higher.aspx'>Number of students taking AP tests up; scores higher</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl7_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">9/3/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            ​More Kentucky students are taking rigorous <a href="https&#58;//apstudent.collegeboard.org/home">Advanced Placement</a> (AP) tests and scoring higher according to data released today from the <a href="https&#58;//apstudent.collegeboard.org/home">College Board</a>. See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R15-097AP-SAT.pdf">news release</a> for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/KDE-seeking-individuals-to-serve-on-teacher-tribunals.aspx'>KDE seeking individuals to serve on teacher tribunals</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl8_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">9/2/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            <p><span></span>The Kentucky Department of Education (KDE) is seeking educators and non-educators interested in serving on teacher tribunals. See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/15-096%20Tribunal%20advisory%20final.pdf">news release​</a> for more information. <br></p>
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/More-Kentucky-graduates-meet-state-benchmarks-on-ACT.aspx'>More Kentucky graduates meet state benchmarks on ACT</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl9_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">8/26/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            More Kentucky public high school graduates are meeting the state’s college-readiness benchmarks on the ACT college-entrance exam, according to data released today by the Kentucky Department of Education. See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R%2015-091%20ACT%202015%20grads.pdf">news release</a> for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/Kentucky-Board-of-Education-reviews-Commissioner-applicants;-selects-Interim-Commissioner.aspx'>Kentucky Board of Education reviews Commissioner applicants; selects Interim Commissioner</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl10_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">8/5/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            At its meeting today, the Kentucky Board of Education conducted its first review of applicants for the position of commissioner of education. See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R15-078%20commissioner%20search-interim%20named.pdf">news release </a>for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    <li>
        <h4><a href='http://education.ky.gov/head/Pages/Public-feedback-sought-on-proposed-Social-Studies-Standards.aspx'>Public feedback sought on proposed Social Studies Standards</a></h4>
        <p id="ctl00_m_g_5e852318_03cd_499b_af58_f4749d431176_ctl00_PageList_ctrl11_pubDateTop" class="pubDate pubDateTop">8/4/2015 12:00:00 AM</p>
        <div class="pageDescription">
            The Kentucky Department of Education (KDE) is seeking public feedback on proposed Social Studies Standards for the Next Generation. See <a href="/comm/news/Documents/R15-077%20Social%20study%20standards%20review.pdf">news release</a> for more information.
        </div>
        
    </li>
  
    </ul>
  
</div>
